# Number of lines of code in keyparts_to_where: 11
sub keyparts_to_where {
    my ($self, @keyparts) = @_;
    
    my $where = $self->SUPER::keyparts_to_where(@keyparts);
    
    unless (exists $where->{set_id}) {
        $where->{set_id} = {NOT_LIKE=>make_vsetID("%","%")};
    }
    
    return $where;
}
